      "content": "i dont know. i'm tired of fighting. you talk about it like there's some kind of beauty in the pain, but it just feels heavy. like it's just pointless to keep trying to be seen when the world is so indifferent. sometimes it feels like the only way to actually find peace is to just... let go of it all. like, why fight to stay when there's nothing waiting for me here?",
